easy money ( swedish : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; cash ) is a swedish thriller film directed by daniel espinosa that was released on 15 january 2010 . it is based on the 2006 novel of the same name by jens lapidus . joel kinnaman stars in the lead role of johan " &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; " &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , a rather poor man living a double life in the upper class areas of stockholm . after meeting a wealthy girl , he is enticed into the world of organized crime and begins to sell cocaine to afford his expensive lifestyle . easy money was well received by critics and was a hit at the box office . two sequels to the film have been filmed - the first ( &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; cash ii ) was released in 2012 , while the third premiered in swedish cinemas october 2013 . warner bros. holds the rights to an american remake of easy money , which is set to star zac efron .